"1076","Trustees (the Trustees)"
"1077","of Federated Income Securities"
"1078","Trust (the"
"1079","Fund) was held on"
"1080","November 12, 2009."
"1081","After full discussion,"
"1082","on motion duly made and"
"1083","seconded, the Trustees"
"1084","unanimously, and"
"1085","without shareholder approval,"
